headline: REPAY Appoints New Chief Financial Officer
summary: ATLANTA, August 11, 2025--Repay Holdings Corporation (NASDAQ: RPAY) ("REPAY" or the "Company"), a leading provider of integrated payment processing solutions, today announced the appointment of Robert Houser as Chief Financial Officer of the Company, effective September 8, 2025.
